  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们这套教育平台的核心数据流，我想从学生数据库开始画起。学生信息存在Education_StudentDB里，这是整个系统的源头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，StudentDB作为起点。那数据从StudentDB出去之后，下一步是流向哪里？是直接到课堂服务，还是中间有内容分发环节？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "中间有个Education_ContentCDN，课件、视频资源都存在那里。学生DB主要是同步用户画像和权限信息给CDN，CDN再根据这些做内容推荐。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "所以StudentDB到ContentCDN是一条数据流，对吧？然后CDN再往下到课堂服务？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，CDN把匹配好的课程内容推给Education_ClassroomService，这样老师进课堂时，学生看到的已经是个性化加载好的界面了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把这三个节点按TB布局排好，StudentDB放最上面，CDN居中，ClassroomService在底部，连线方向从上到下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，我刚才说的顺序可能让你误解了。不是StudentDB直接连ClassroomService，而是必须经CDN中转。你现在的连线是不是跳过了CDN？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我调整一下：StudentDB只连到CDN，CDN再连到ClassroomService，形成两条先后依赖的边，没有跨层连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "这样就对了。整个流程就是学生数据驱动内容分发，CDN做缓冲和个性化，最后课堂服务呈现。这个结构清晰多了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
